latestPosts.caption:
One of the best birthday gift 💝 

I’ve never shared this before but let me tell you one thing .

I belong from tea garden (sepoy dhoora T:E near rongtong)

Growing up I never thought I could do something like this,I was always interested in entertainment field but had no hopes that I could do anything in this field ,bcz everyone around me bullied me saying I was a hopeless child and I had no bright future ahead (bcz meh suffer kr rhi the mom dad kam k Lea city shift ho gye the and that time financially Itna strong nhi the ki mujhe city meh padne mile)

My mom dad did everything possible and meko v 2 years badd city n shift krwa dea 

after I graduated I started giving auditions for tv Ads ,Tollywood serial,I did some print shoots for brands but then lockdown happened.

I was clear in my head that 9-5 is not my cup of tea ☕️ 
I think god gave me chance q ki jab meri job Karne ki bari ayi lockdown lag gya,so I started my YouTube channel on 14th july 2021 ,and I started posting on Instagram too,till then I had no clue ki yaha kya hota h,kaise hota h aaur yaha earning v hoti h

I started doing it bcz I love to be in front of camera.
Narayan had bigger and better plans 💕

It still feels surreal that I won this award 🏆

All thanks to my audience,you guys are my strength,you have given me everything once I had dreamed of.

Secondly I would like to thank my mom ,dad and my family who has been there for me in every aspect of my life.

Also huge shoutout to @inspiriaindia  @callme___md 
For acknowledging the talents,I’m really very grateful to you guys.

Lastly bs yahi khena hai dream big and start taking small step towards it ,you will achieve ever single dream of yours 💕

Thank you,
Xoxo sudiksha.
